(1, 10060, 9, 256, '4', 'Decent', 'Decent product, works as described. Satisfied!', 1, 2, '2020-09-29 11:36:48', '2020-09-29 11:28:36', '2020-09-29 11:36:48'),
(2, 10060, 9, 273, '5', 'Awesome!', 'Great parfum, a bit expensive but worth it.', 1, 2, '2020-09-29 11:37:05', '2020-09-29 11:36:01', '2020-10-01 11:35:56'),
(3, 10052, 9, 24, '4', 'Size Up If You Have Any Upper Body Strength', 'I just bought this on pre-sale and had to size up. I have a 30 pound, elderly dog (that I lift up and down stairs, in and out of cars), ride a motorcycle and work out at the gym, so my upper body may be larger than average. I had to size up in order to accommodate my shoulders, arms and chest.\nOther than that, the colors are beautiful. The photo doesn\'t do the dress justice, The orange flowers pop on the dark blue background. The blue looks navy in the photo but it\'s more like midnight. Truly a beautiful pattern. Keep in mind that each dress is unique, depending on how the material is cut to sew seams. So, try on more than one and it will look different, depending on the placement of the flowers.\nOther than having to swallow my pride and go up a size, it\'s a winner.\nI do wish there were more offerings with the front zipper and short sleeves. The front zipper helps take the pressure off tightness in the shoulders/arms/chest area. The sleeves help camouflage large biceps.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 09:55:52', '2020-10-01 11:36:40', '2020-10-16 09:55:52'),
(4, 10053, 9, 116, '3', 'Comfy Cool', 'These slip on sneakers are super comfortable and cute. I liked them so much that I ended up buying 2 pairs of the camo print, one for my daughter and one for me. Easy cool all the way!', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 09:56:00', '2020-10-01 15:12:46', '2020-10-16 09:56:00'),
(5, 10059, 9, 214, '5', 'Beautiful!', 'This is as beautiful as it can get.. Classy!', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 09:56:08', '2020-10-01 15:33:41', '2020-10-16 09:56:08'),
(6, 10054, 9, 119, '4', 'Oh No!', 'These shoes are cute and the color is just everything. I wanted to love them ( I ordered 2 pair) but they are just too tight. I do have somewhat wide feet, but I have other ugg slides and slippers that fit just fine, so I believe it is this shoe. I the strap closest to the ankle is what bothers me. There is no stretch at all for the straps that go over the foot (the sling back elastic is perfect). I am going to keep them and hope that with a little wear they will give and be a little more comfortable. Sizing up would\'ve been way to long so I wont, but if you have wide feet these might not be the best slide for you. I do recommend them because they are cute and stylish. Just use your best judgement on sizing.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 09:56:14', '2020-10-01 15:34:34', '2020-10-16 09:56:14'),
(7, 10054, 9, 173, '5', 'Quality jacket', 'Super pleased with this purchase. The jacket arrived quickly and is much warmer than I anticipated - it will be great to wear well into the fall. I\'m glad that I took other reviewers\' recommendations to size up. This jacket definitely runs small! I\'m normally a size S and purchased a size M. It fits great but would be hard to squeeze a sweatshirt under. If you want to be able to wear bulkier layers underneath the jacket, it would be worth going up two sizes.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 09:56:20', '2020-10-01 15:37:36', '2020-10-16 09:56:20'),
(8, 10053, 9, 259, '4', 'Great buy', 'Makes eyelashes look so much fuller! I love them! Were them as often as possible!!', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 09:56:25', '2020-10-01 15:42:32', '2020-10-16 09:56:25'),
(9, 10053, 9, 261, '2', 'Okay for some', 'Made my eyelashes hurt, very heavy and irritated my eyes. Hard to remove ALL of the mascara and my eye make up remover always takes off any other mascara I have used. Probably okay for some individuals. It did make my lashes long.....but felt weird and heavy.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 09:56:34', '2020-10-01 15:44:19', '2020-10-16 09:56:34'),
(10, 10052, 9, 231, '4', 'Pretty earring.', 'The earrings look nice on and much nicer in person. The tricolor is not so outstanding like the picture but more muted.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 09:56:40', '2020-10-01 15:50:21', '2020-10-16 09:56:40'),
(11, 10048, 9, 130, '1', 'Phone did not fit', 'Darling purse, Great Value, but I had to return it, as my phone did not fit.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:10:37', '2020-10-01 15:51:18', '2020-10-16 13:10:37'),
(12, 10044, 9, 72, '3', 'Flexibility', 'Too tight across top of foot. If the band across the foot was flexible or manual it would be more comfortable for the consumer because they will be able to adjust the tension.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:10:30', '2020-10-01 15:52:21', '2020-10-16 13:10:30'),
(13, 10045, 9, 72, '3', 'Flexibility', 'Too tight across top of foot. If the band across the foot was flexible or manual it would be more comfortable for the consumer because they will be able to adjust the tension.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:10:24', '2020-10-01 15:53:47', '2020-10-16 13:10:24'),
(14, 10043, 9, 199, '5', 'timeless beauty', 'Simply stunning. More beautiful in person. Picture does not do this ring justice. I seen in store tried on & had to make mine. I am petite ( 5ft, 100 lbs). I wear this ring on middle finger. This ring design is very unique & classy. So happy to own. I wear slightly at angle to show all the sparkling diamonds', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:10:17', '2020-10-01 15:54:52', '2020-10-16 13:10:17'),
(15, 10052, 9, 148, '5', 'Love Hue Tights -the BEST!', 'Always love Hue tights, never a complaint -except their really thick/winter tights that show the shiny lycra. These tights are PERFECT, no shine, opaque and light enough to wear in Southern California! Gives you enough color without a ton of coverage. Really slightly above a nylon, but much longer lasting. I highly recommend for Fall/Winter/Spring. Will buy another pair as back up. Bought the black -those are awesome too. Hue quality is great -hands down.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:10:10', '2020-10-01 16:01:36', '2020-10-16 13:10:10'),
(16, 10053, 9, 268, '5', 'Love It', 'The packaging is what sold me at first site but then the actual lipsticks are amazing as well. Of course since they are MAC, a staple in the beauty industry. A must have for your collection.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:10:03', '2020-10-01 16:03:18', '2020-10-16 13:10:03'),
(17, 10043, 9, 108, '5', 'Sexy and comfortable', 'Great quality, true to size, soooo comfortable! I’m back on ordering in another color. I got the denim and they’re absolutely beautiful, couldn’t be happier.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:09:54', '2020-10-01 16:03:57', '2020-10-16 13:09:54'),
(18, 10052, 9, 83, '5', 'Leather upper and Fantastic Deal', 'I bought the tan ones and I love them. I usually can\'t wear heels because I have issues with my arch from over wearing heels when I was younger. I\'m 42 and they are so comfortable and still kind of sexy.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:09:38', '2020-10-01 16:05:01', '2020-10-16 13:09:38'),
(19, 10048, 9, 124, '5', 'I want one for myself and I am not pregnant!!', 'Absolutely perfect diaper bag. Lots of room for everything and very stylish!! It can even be used for an overnight bag!!', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:09:13', '2020-10-01 16:06:16', '2020-10-16 13:09:13'),
(20, 10047, 9, 269, '4', 'Pretty good!', 'Ill start with the only negative - it could be somewhat more pigmented. Its really not a bad color payoff but you definitely need to build the lightest shade (possibly the others two light ones depending on preference). I did take off a star because for a palette it couldve wowed more but honestly I think part of the price is for the name.\nPros: again still good payoff (just not the best Ive seen), blends very easily, is super versatile for day and night. As an added plus, the packaging is great - pretty and sturdy enough for me to feel safe traveling with it, definitely great quality.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:09:06', '2020-10-01 16:09:42', '2020-10-16 13:09:06'),
(21, 10044, 9, 144, '4', 'great sporty alternative', 'I love how the stripe on these Spanx leggings add flair for a more sporty look. I like to wear them with white sneakers and a white button-down tunic. they fit true to size but really hold you in :)', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:08:52', '2020-10-01 16:19:13', '2020-10-16 13:08:52'),
(22, 10051, 9, 58, '5', 'Very Comfortable', 'Cheap, easy, chic & comfortable. 10/10!', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:08:40', '2020-10-01 16:25:26', '2020-10-16 13:08:40'),
(23, 10047, 9, 272, '4', 'I Love it!!', 'This is one of the best perfumes I have ever bought. I love the aroma, it is soft but very fine. I have been using it for 4 years, I recommend it.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:08:34', '2020-10-01 16:33:09', '2020-10-16 13:08:34'),
(24, 10051, 9, 174, '5', 'Flattering & Stylish Raincoat', 'Beautiful coat I got for a trip to Ireland this spring. It\'s lightweight but warm with a feminine fit. The length is perfect and I love the collar with the hood up and down. Very happy with my purchase', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:08:28', '2020-10-01 16:34:42', '2020-10-16 13:08:28'),
(25, 10050, 9, 10, '3', 'Gap in the back and waistband too low', 'I am a curvy fit gal and finding jeans is a pain in the you know what. They stopped making my previous favorites and I needed a ... ahem... bigger size. These are made well but do not fit a curvy figure (mine anyway) very well... the straight leg version is MUCH better. the 414 Levi model. Check them out. Love them... These gap in the back and the waistband is too low so they feel like they are falling off when you bend over. Can\'t recommend them. They are going back.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:08:14', '2020-10-01 16:39:05', '2020-10-16 13:08:14'),
(26, 10047, 9, 99, '3', 'Vibrant colors', 'Beautiful colors, fits well BUT these are the most uncomfortable thongs I have ever had on my feet. The thong is a very hard plastic and is very uncomfortable. I will sadly be returning these.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:08:04', '2020-10-01 16:40:21', '2020-10-16 13:08:04'),
(27, 10042, 9, 194, '5', 'Trendy Watch', 'Lacoste can\'t go wrong. Very classy watch', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:07:54', '2020-10-01 16:41:19', '2020-10-16 13:07:54'),
(28, 10050, 9, 41, '4', 'Perfect fit', 'Love these shorts! Perfect fit, true to size. Hoping to wear them on vacation this summer. Definitely would purchase them again.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:07:46', '2020-10-01 16:44:44', '2020-10-16 13:07:46'),
(29, 10050, 9, 39, '2', 'Not Really Impressed', 'Material is a bit heavier than expected. The waist has a drawstring but is tight. The description should\'ve recommended ordering a size up.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:07:13', '2020-10-01 16:47:29', '2020-10-16 13:07:13'),
(30, 10048, 9, 164, '5', 'Love at first sight!', 'I haphazardly stumbled across these Gucci frames and boy am I in love.. the sunglasses are beautifully designed. I love the mirrored look and the frame compliments my round face perfectly.. I can only imagine that it will be a hit and talk of conversation amongst my friends as I already received a compliments from passersbys when I tried them on in the store. I’m so excited and I can’t wait for fun in the sun while rocking my Gucci!', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:07:06', '2020-10-01 16:56:02', '2020-10-16 13:07:06'),
(31, 10049, 9, 97, '3', 'Very flattering for short walks', 'Very pretty sandals. They however feel a bit snug between my toes and would feel uncomfortable with time. They are stylish to wear but since they have no arch support for my size10 I can wear for a short period. They are visually pretty to wear', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:06:52', '2020-10-01 16:57:32', '2020-10-16 13:06:52'),
(32, 10046, 9, 235, '5', 'Perfect! Lightweight and stylish!', 'I am in love with my earrings very elegant price is reasonable.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:06:44', '2020-10-01 16:58:26', '2020-10-16 13:06:44'),
(33, 10046, 9, 193, '4', 'Very cute watch', 'I have comparatively smaller wrist. This watch is perfect for me. I love it. It is a cute watch with smaller dial. If you are looking for medium or big dial, don\'t go for it.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:06:37', '2020-10-01 16:59:43', '2020-10-16 13:06:37'),
(34, 10045, 9, 144, '5', 'Spanx all day any day anywhere', 'These leggings were super comfortable. I wore them as travel pants from cold climate to warm. I expected them to get hot once I reached my destination - they were not!!! They are flattering and can be dressed up or down! Absolutely love them.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:06:31', '2020-10-01 17:00:31', '2020-10-16 13:06:31'),
(35, 10028, 8, 211, '4', 'Simple and elegant', 'Gifted this and a birthday gift, so elegant and vintage looking. Girlfriend loved the color and simplicity', 1, 2, '2020-10-19 17:32:47', '2020-10-01 17:18:27', '2020-10-19 17:32:47'),
(36, 10028, 8, 216, '4', 'Perfect gift', 'It was a gift for my daughter and she loved it so much.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:06:13', '2020-10-01 17:19:11', '2020-10-16 13:06:13'),
(37, 10027, 8, 143, '5', 'best product ever', 'Wife gained a little weight and was self conscious of it. She wanted to wear a fitted blouse, but waist didn\'t go in as it once did. She wore the Spanx. When she arrived at the affair, two women looked at her and said, \"Did you lose weight\"? The chart according to her weight says a medium but a small fits better. Maybe it is because she don\'t have a fat behind and is 5\'2\'\'. Love it. Also it makes her back feel good, kind of makes her stand up straighter. What woman doesn\'t want a compliment and from another woman, no less. That is saying it all.', 1, 2, '2020-10-19 17:32:58', '2020-10-01 17:20:05', '2020-10-19 17:32:58'),
(38, 10027, 8, 39, '4', 'Very Comfy', 'Very comfortable athletic shorts. Nice color options..', 1, 2, '2020-10-19 17:33:07', '2020-10-01 17:23:13', '2020-10-19 17:33:07'),
(39, 10026, 8, 94, '5', 'Best fit for comfort and spring to fall sandal.', 'Comfort and fit is perfect; adjusts if needed. Sister likes her sandal to stay on this one is attractive & functional. She has this sandal in two colors and just reordered 3 more now. Lived it and highly recommended this comfortable fitting Sandal.', 1, 2, '2020-10-19 17:33:15', '2020-10-01 17:23:57', '2020-10-19 17:33:15'),
(40, 10025, 8, 24, '4', 'Flattering cut and fit', 'Daughter loved everything about this dress except the color of the flowers -- more coral than pink -- which did not suit her coloring, alas. Also, the large print was a little overwhelming on her 5\"2\" frame. Hoping that DNKY comes out with this same dress in a different print soon, so I returned it.', 1, 2, '2020-10-19 17:33:20', '2020-10-01 17:25:19', '2020-10-19 17:33:20'),
(41, 10025, 8, 137, '5', 'Very handy', 'Nice comfortable socks. Easy to wear all day..', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:05:16', '2020-10-01 17:26:55', '2020-10-16 13:05:16'),
(42, 10025, 8, 140, '3', 'got a run on day 1?', 'Feels great, but got a run in my wives stocking on the first day. Come on... paying enough that they should have a very sturdy fabric to prevent runs. jeez', 1, 2, '2020-10-19 17:33:33', '2020-10-01 17:27:29', '2020-10-19 17:33:33'),
(43, 10024, 8, 208, '3', 'Is uncomfortable to wear', 'The stone is pretty but the band is so narrow that it shifts on your finger. The diamonds scratch the sides of your other fingers and the band makes it look cheap. (courtesy: my wife)', 1, 2, '2020-10-19 17:33:41', '2020-10-01 17:28:33', '2020-10-19 17:33:41'),
(44, 10024, 8, 296, '3', 'Like The Product', 'This product works well for my mother\'s dried flaky skin, makes her look fresh, and reduces fine lines. Nice fresh lemon scent. The bad thing is it makes her breakout! She doesn\'t recommend if you have acne prone skin. Otherwise, i would\'ve given it 5 stars.', 1, 2, '2020-10-19 17:33:48', '2020-10-01 17:29:30', '2020-10-19 17:33:48'),
(45, 10030, 7, 128, '5', 'The Most Adorable Small Crossbody Bag!', 'I absolutely LOVE this little crossbody bag! The graffiti print design is so urban chic and unique, I can\'t go anywhere without getting compliments on this bag. The leather is nice and it fits my essentials, even my large smartphone! I love carrying it!', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:03:12', '2020-10-01 17:30:32', '2020-10-16 13:03:12'),
(46, 10030, 7, 125, '5', 'Nice Backpack for Everyday Use', 'Really enjoy using this backpack. It is nicely designed with minimal distracting elements and has a ton of space. I needed to use bring about 5 different athletic outfits (yoga pants + top + sports bras) and was very pleased that I could fit all of my outfits into the main pocket and my wallet + phone + keys + chapstick in the front pocket. Definitely a go-to backpack for me.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:03:07', '2020-10-01 17:31:49', '2020-10-16 13:03:07'),
(47, 10029, 7, 179, '4', 'surprisingly nice jacket', 'I received this jacket and was pleasantly surprised by the quality and style. It was nicer than I expected. It is trendy and sporty, but unfortunately big on me. I do recommend the product though for any age group.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:04:47', '2020-10-01 17:59:53', '2020-10-16 13:04:47'),
(48, 10029, 7, 61, '4', 'Beautiful but size not accurate', 'They are really beautiful, but definitely order a half size up! Also, be aware that the color is much brighter than the picture. It seems more like a vivid type of pink than pale pink.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:02:55', '2020-10-01 18:00:31', '2020-10-16 13:02:55'),
(49, 10008, 7, 8, '2', 'These are a NO for me...', 'I was excited to get these track pants. However, I knew when I saw the LOOK of the pants, they were going back. I normally wear a Large: I am 5\'6 and 170lbs. I am curvy. But after reading the reviews, I ordered the black in Medium. I should have gotten a Small. These are a super weird cut. The thigh area is balloon big and the area below the knee is narrow and fitted. The waist area was also fitted. O yeah, returned asap.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:02:49', '2020-10-01 18:01:45', '2020-10-16 13:02:49'),
(50, 10008, 7, 70, '5', 'Rose Gold Nike in Pink', 'Wonderful running shoes. Whether you\'re running, or moving at a walking pace, these shoes will get you there. I will be saving these for the marathon I hope to run one day, maybe if I can wait that long.\nI tried them out for the first time, the day they were delivered and I am completely in awe of them. Not a large amount of arch support; so, grab yourself a good pair of arch support socks, if you need extra arch support. Otherwise, this pair is a wonderful performing shoe for your favorite exercise routine. Exercise is not odd or \"weird\" right now! Go get some exercise. Cheers!', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 13:02:42', '2020-10-01 18:03:13', '2020-10-16 13:02:42'),
(51, 10008, 7, 186, '5', 'Gorgeous watch!', 'I have many Fossil watches and I love them all. This one is especially lovely and very unique. I have never had a problem with Fossil watches and find them to be of excellent quality. I love the large watch face and easy to read numbers.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 12:47:48', '2020-10-01 18:03:51', '2020-10-16 12:47:48'),
(52, 10007, 7, 30, '5', 'Beautiful', 'Chic & rusty, but class apart. I look Hot!', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 12:47:42', '2020-10-01 18:06:24', '2020-10-16 12:47:42'),
(53, 10007, 7, 81, '5', 'Low but sexy heel', 'This shoe looks really sexy on. My husband absolutely loved them on me. Don\'t let the low heel fool you. It looks amazing on and super comfortable. The strap can be worn higher up on the ankle or just wrapped around low on the ankle. I bought the black and they look great dressed up or even with jeans. So glad I purchased.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 12:47:36', '2020-10-01 18:06:58', '2020-10-16 12:47:36'),
(54, 10006, 7, 36, '4', 'Real cute, comfortable and stylish skirt', 'I love this skirt! I can’t believe how comfortable it is to wear. Then when I wear it I don’t just feel the comfort but feel stylish and sexy at the same time. I am 5’2” and I love the length since I don’t like short skirts. The only drawback is that the ribbon in the side of the skirt (the upper part) gives a bumpy look. But I still love it and highly recommend it!', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 12:47:30', '2020-10-01 18:08:55', '2020-10-16 12:47:30'),
(55, 10006, 7, 41, '4', 'Comfortable', 'These are my new favorite casual shorts. They are very comfortable! I wear a size 8 and ordered a medium and the shorts are slightly large, but i would rather they be a little loose than a little tight.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 12:47:22', '2020-10-01 18:10:11', '2020-10-16 12:47:22'),
(56, 10006, 7, 119, '3', 'Foot keeps slipping to the side', '1. All eyes are on these, because they\'re really fashionable and the color yellow I chose is really unique. 2. Comfortable but after frequent use the fluffiness fades and it feels like you\'re walking on a block. 3. I bought my usual size but my foot isn\'t kept in place, so it often slides to the sides and makes walking a bit tricky.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 12:47:12', '2020-10-01 18:14:15', '2020-10-16 12:47:12'),
(57, 10029, 7, 172, '3', 'Very heavy fabric', 'The polyester outer fabric is excellent quality; sewn in lining is thin, woven polyester; washable. No removable liner. The extreme weight of the raincoat was uncomfortable and could be worn in 30 degree F. weather. I prefer to wear this type of polyester raincoat in the fall and spring 50-65 degree F. temps around the town but this was way too heavy. The raglan sleeves sort of puffed up at the top was not attractive on me as the coat fits large to begin with.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 12:46:59', '2020-10-03 14:39:26', '2020-10-16 12:46:59'),
(58, 10032, 6, 261, '1', 'Giant disappointment.', 'Clumpy and doesn\'t do much at all for my lashes. I\'m extremely disappointed in this product. Not worth the money.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 12:46:54', '2020-10-03 14:59:01', '2020-10-16 12:46:54'),
(59, 10032, 6, 247, '5', 'Great , the best', 'Awesome unbelievable the best dryer and iron thank you T3 , I recommend it,', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 12:46:48', '2020-10-03 15:00:19', '2020-10-16 12:46:48'),
(60, 10032, 6, 248, '5', 'One of a kind!', 'My brother has one of these as a hairdresser. I like to just sit and brush my hair with it just because it feels SO NICE! So great on my thick, long, curly hair! It\'s gentle but strong at the same time. Wish I had my own.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 12:46:42', '2020-10-03 15:01:17', '2020-10-16 12:46:42'),
(61, 10031, 6, 113, '5', 'Beautiful', 'Elegant, lightweight, and class!', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 12:46:33', '2020-10-03 15:03:56', '2020-10-16 12:46:33'),
(62, 10031, 6, 165, '5', 'stylish', 'i love them, very stylish and very light, i am a happy customer, thank you!', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 12:46:26', '2020-10-03 15:04:23', '2020-10-16 12:46:26'),
(63, 10011, 6, 102, '5', 'Pewter shoes go with EVERY Outfit!!', 'I Buy every style In Clarks sandals Pewter OR Gold ~ Why Not ? they match EVERY out fit! Great with skinny jeans~ capris, Bermuda shorts~ ETC! ~ My toes Nails are getting done this weekend..LOL', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 12:46:20', '2020-10-03 15:06:21', '2020-10-16 12:46:20'),
(64, 10010, 6, 34, '4', 'Stylish skort', 'Very cute skort. Goes with lots of tops. I gave it 4 stars because the red belt is very cheap so it doesn’t add anything to it.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 12:46:13', '2020-10-03 15:06:55', '2020-10-16 12:46:13'),
(65, 10010, 6, 158, '2', 'Arms too loose', 'OK sunglasses but arms are way too loose. Nothing special so returned.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 12:45:37', '2020-10-03 15:07:56', '2020-10-16 12:45:37'),
(66, 10010, 6, 135, '5', 'Love This Bag.', 'Got this for a great price. Always a fan of Calvin Klein bags. This one is well made and has logical storage areas.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 12:45:31', '2020-10-03 15:08:41', '2020-10-16 12:45:31'),
(67, 10010, 6, 146, '3', 'The sizing is not consistant', 'I bought these in the black and white. They are nice tights, but the fabric is somewhat thin. I expected thicker fabric.\nMore importantly, even though I bought two different colors in a size three, the black ones were stretchier than the white ones, and hence were a tad bigger. The white ones were too small. I could barely get them on. The fabric was not as giving.\nIn my opinion, the sizing is misleading. A size three should be able to fit someone who is up to 6 feet tall, 200 pounds. I am much smaller than that, and the size three ran tight on me. If you buy these, I suggest choosing at least one size up.', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 12:45:26', '2020-10-03 15:09:26', '2020-10-16 12:45:26'),
(68, 10010, 6, 147, '5', 'Cute!', 'Cute socks for a great price! My daughter is a 10 and loves her socks!', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 12:45:20', '2020-10-03 15:12:09', '2020-10-16 12:45:20'),
