(74, 10033, 5, 101, '5', 'WOW! Very Comfortable, Classy Sandals! LOVE IT!!', 'It’s hard to find a classy, sexy pair of sandals that are also very comfortable for the feet, and doesn’t tire your legs out. The heel is just right...not too high, not too low. High quality materials, real leather, with cushioned base. Fits beautifully. Love the simplistic, but classy design! Light weight, doesn’t drag around like some of those heavier based wedged sandals. Has a nice rubber traction under the sandals to prevent from slipping. Plus it gives a quieter step when walking on tile, wooden floors, etc. Highly recommend!', 1, 2, '2020-10-16 12:44:34', '2020-10-03 15:20:23', '2020-10-16 12:44:34'),
