(115, 10005, 1, 96, '4', 'Nice for price-point', 'I was looking for a cute casual sandal I could wear with both jeans, casual dresses and shorts. My feet are a bit narrow, but not narrow enough for a narrow fit. These have a slightly padded foot bed, no arch support and I find the upper strap to be a bit wide for my foot, but they\'re comfortable despite that and I\'ll mix them in with other sandals to extend the wear. I\'ve only had them a couple of days, so I can\'t comment on the quality, but because I bought them on sale, I feel they were a good deal. I usually wear a 7-7.5 and the 7 fit better for me. I\'ve gotten several compliments on them.', 1, 2, '2020-10-15 18:06:51', '2020-10-03 16:41:14', '2020-10-15 18:06:51'),
